Title: ECE: Misc: Grainger Scholarship
Body: Date: Mon, 11 Nov 1996 21:12:24 GMT Server: NCSA/1.5 Content-type: text/html ECE: Misc: Grainger Scholarship College of Engineering University of Wisconsin - Madison Electrical and Computer Engineering T he Grainger Foundation has established a major new award program for UW-Madison students who earn an undergraduate or graduate degree with a specialization in electric power engineering.
